item.description: navigation-bar # The page navigation bar configuration node is used to specify some properties of the navigation bar. It can only be the first node in the page-meta component, and it needs to be used together. Property description Attributes Types of Defaults Required Description title-icon string no Title icon, icon path such as “./img/t.png”, only supports local file path, relative path, relative to the host position of the current page, fixed width and height are logical pixel value “34px”.
